title: Seekers Alliance - 👤│role-book
html:
# Role Book

- 🔑 Admin - Seekers Alliance core team
- 🎩 Elite Seeker - Our wonderful community mods - ask them for help!
- 🌟 OG Seeker - Our earliest supporters with special benefits (TBD)
- 🆎 EN-speaker - English-speaking Seekers (for targeted notifications)
- 🀄 CN-speaker - Chinese-speaking Seekers (for targeted notifications)
- ⭐ Seeker - A member of the Seekers Alliance (verified users)
- 🏆Champion Lvl1-Lvl10 - Seekers who won 1 or more events (for future raffles & benefits)
- 🏅Truth Seeker - Seekers who placed top 10 in #pop-quiz
